snippet.title: WUCHANG: Fallen Feathers - Official Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview October 2024
snippet.description:
This trailer showcases new action-packed gameplay featuring intense combat against wicked bosses, the unleashing of devastating abilities, haunting environments, and stunning CGI visuals that prepare you for the experience that awaits. Delve deeper into the game's rich narrative and learn more about the Ming Inspector boss who is waiting to add you to his collection. 

WUCHANG: Fallen Feathers is a soulslike action-RPG that will push you to the limits as you face off against an onslaught of monstrous creatures. Unravel the secrets of your forgotten past in the land of Shu before you are consumed by the Feathering disease. Launching day one with Xbox Game Pass in 2025. Join the WUCHANG community today and be part of the adventure!
